title: Hour 2 - NBA Player Stagnation, Joe LaCava
itunes:title: Hour 2 - NBA Player Stagnation, Joe LaCava
description:
Dan discusses the distinct lack of movement by NBA players after James Harden agrees to stay in Philadelphia. And he talks to Tiger Woods' caddy, Joe LaCava.
